%h1 New rsvp

%h2
  Hello! You're here because you got an invitation.
  %br
  Just fill out the form below to let us know if you're coming.

%p We either can't wait to see you, or you're dead to us!

- if @rsvp.errors.any?
  .error_explanation
    %h2
      - pluralize(@rsvp.errors.count, "error")
      stopped us from saving your RSVP.
    %ul
      - @rsvp.errors.full_messages.each do |err|
        %li= err

=form_for :rsvps, url: rsvps_path do |f|
  %p
    = f.label :names
    %i Enter your names, separated by a comma
    = f.text_field :names


  %p
    = f.label :food_choice
    = f.text_field :food_choice


  %p
    = f.label :attending
    %i "True" or "False"
    = f.text_field :attending

  %p
    = f.submit
